
Overview of adj hearty

The adj hearty has 5 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (1) hearty -- (showing warm and heartfelt friendliness; "gave us a cordial reception"; "a hearty welcome")
2. hearty, satisfying, solid, square, substantial -- (providing abundant nourishment; "a hearty meal"; "good solid food"; "ate a substantial breakfast"; "four square meals a day")
3. hearty, full-blooded, lusty, red-blooded -- (endowed with or exhibiting great bodily or mental health; "a hearty glow of health")
4. hearty -- (consuming abundantly and with gusto; "a hearty (or healthy) appetite")
5. hearty -- (without reservation; "hearty support")
